title: Aly Raisman Shows Off Her Sexy Side in Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue Photos
text: Yahoo Celebrity February 18, 2017 Aly Raisman is a rock star among gymnasts. At 22, she’s racked up six medals at two Olympics, a feat that she accomplished by following a seriously disciplined workout for most of her life. In the 2017 Sports Illustrated swimsuit Issue , which is on sale now, she shows off the strong and sexy body she’s achieved.
